trans-unit.source: Provides style capability for the pagination UI of a page.
trans-unit.target: 页的分页 UI 提供样式功能。

trans-unit.source: For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see the [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web site.
trans-unit.target: 了解如何开发 ASP.NET 移动应用程序的信息，请参阅[www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web 站点。

trans-unit.source: The PagerStyle object is a <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Style> object with additional style properties specific to the pagination user interface (UI) of a form.
trans-unit.target: PagerStyle 对象是<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Style>具有其他样式属性特定于窗体的分页用户界面 (UI) 对象。</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: Use the properties and methods of the PagerStyle class to override default text for the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.NextPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PreviousPageText%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PageLabel%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: 使用属性和 PagerStyle 类的方法来重写的默认文本<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.NextPageText%2A>， <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PreviousPageText%2A>，和<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PageLabel%2A>属性。</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PageLabel%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PreviousPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.NextPageText%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you are programmatically creating a form with Next and Previous links to the appropriate pages, you can override the text for these links by setting the value of the properties previously mentioned.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果你要以编程方式创建一个窗体，而的相应页面的下一步和上一页链接，你可以重写的文本这些链接前面提到的属性的值设置。

trans-unit.source: You can use methods, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetNextPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetPreviousPageText%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetPageLabelText%2A> to retrieve the current value of the properties.
trans-unit.target: 你可以使用方法，如<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetNextPageText%2A>， <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetPreviousPageText%2A>，或<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetPageLabelText%2A>检索属性的当前值。</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetPageLabelText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetPreviousPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.GetNextPageText%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PageLabel%2A> property applies only to HTML markup and may not be rendered in other markups such as WML.
trans-unit.target: 1> [!NOTE]&1;><xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PageLabel%2A>属性仅适用于 HTML 标记并且可能不会呈现在 WML 等其他标记。</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PagerStyle.PageLabel%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the label used for the current page.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置用于当前页的标签。

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: 默认值为空字符串 ("")。

trans-unit.source: This API is obsolete.
trans-unit.target: 此 API 已废弃不用。

trans-unit.source: For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see the [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web site.
trans-unit.target: 了解如何开发 ASP.NET 移动应用程序的信息，请参阅[www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web 站点。

trans-unit.source: If this property contains an empty string, no label is displayed.
trans-unit.target: 如果此属性包含一个空字符串，则会不显示任何标签。

trans-unit.source: The label can include the format specifiers `{0}` and `{1}`, which are substituted with the page number of the current page and the total number of pages, respectively, when the label is rendered.
trans-unit.target: 该标签可以包括的格式说明符`{0}`和`{1}`，这会替换为当前页的页码和总页数，分别，标签将呈现时。

trans-unit.source: For example, the format specifier `Page {0} of {1}` would show the current position within the total number of pages.
trans-unit.target: 例如，使用格式说明符`Page {0} of {1}`会显示页的总数中的当前位置。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > WML devices do not render this property.
trans-unit.target: 1> [!NOTE]&1;> WML 设备不会呈现此属性。

trans-unit.source: The label used for the current page.
trans-unit.target: 所用的当前页的标签。
